org.intermine.bio.dataconversion

Class UniprotConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.intermine.dataconversion.DataConverter
      • org.intermine.dataconversion.DirectoryConverter
        • org.intermine.bio.dataconversion.BioDirectoryConverter
          • org.intermine.bio.dataconversion.UniprotConverter

  • public class UniprotConverter
extends BioDirectoryConverter
    DataConverter to parse UniProt data into items. Improved version of UniProtConverter. Differs from UniProtConverter in that this Converter creates proper protein items. UniProtConverter creates protein objects, that are really uniprot entries.

      • parseFileNames

        protected java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.io.File[]> parseFileNames(java.io.File[] fileList)
        sprot data files need to be processed immediately before trembl ones not all organisms are going to have both files UniProtFilterTask has already been run so all files are assumed to be valid. expected syntax : 7227_uniprot_sprot.xml [TAXONID]_uniprot_[SOURCE].xml SOURCE: sprot or trembl
        Parameters:
        fileList - list of files to parse
        Returns:
        list of files ordered to that SwissProt files are parsed first
